{"parentUuid":"2415a2e2-8dc7-41d5-ac29-4fc8d0f2c535","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_013FAvFmLXvneAf2CxWDqSM1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"简短回答：**目前不能通过标准 ACP 协议直接调用**，但可以通过更简单的方式使用。\n\n---\n\n**原因：**\n\nCodex CLI (`codex-cli`) 本身不实现 ACP Server，它是一个交互式 CLI 工具，没有暴露 ACP 兼容的 HTTP/gRPC 端点。ACP 要求 agent 运行一个可发现的服务，Codex 目前不满足这点。\n\n---\n\n**实际可行的方式：**\n\n我可以直接通过 Bash 工具调用本地 `codex` 命令：\n\n```bash\ncodex \"帮我实现 xxx 功能\"\n```\n\n但这有局限：\n- Codex CLI 默认是**交互式**的，不适合无人值守调用\n- 它会消耗你的 OpenAI 额度\n\n---\n\n**如果你想让我在编码任务中使用 Codex，你可以：**\n\n1. 明确告诉我\"这个任务用 codex 来做\"\n2. 我用 `--full-auto` 或非交互模式（如果支持）调用它\n\n你具体想在什么场景下用 Codex？是希望在我处理某类任务时自动委托给它吗？"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":410,"cache_read_input_tokens":18874,"output_tokens":774,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":410,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZYaRGpgskVeBDeqhHVMy","type":"assistant","uuid":"bf2b204f-92c6-4f5a-b47c-79046b878cc1","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:45:34.167Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/xuwentao/Projects/tele/tap-edu-backend/.claude/worktrees/sleepy-burnell","sessionId":"66dcb88e-7507-45ea-9504-f4f667730535","version":"2.1.87","gitBranch":"xuwt5/sleepy-burnell","slug":"reflective-conjuring-curry"}
